%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9e7c527a6f66a8c49a6fab10a94681fc, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day1NightP
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  sequenceId: albert_day1_night_pill
  lines:
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: I just received the completion notice for the tasks. According to DOLOS,
      everything went smoothly. Wiring shows an optimal power flow in that quadrant.
      Good job.
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Yeah, it was fine. Standard grid alignment.
      nextLineIndex: 1
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: Whatever gets the paycheck.
      nextLineIndex: 2
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I\u2019ve said it before, and I\u2019ll say it again. You\u2019ve always
      had a keen eye. That\u2019s why the DOLOS Corporation hired you."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 4
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Heh\u2026 can\u2019t blame you, I guess."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "As long as you complete your work efficiently, DOLOS will remain in a
      satisfactory state. It\u2019s in your best interest to keep it that way."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 4
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: On an unrelated note, the UNEP Annual 2116 Report was released earlier
      this quarter.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 5
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "A bunch of jargon, but also some interesting points about the state of
      the Earth. Don\u2019t know if you kept up with it."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "No, I haven\u2019t kept up with the annual report. And frankly,
        I couldn\u2019t care less about the Earth."
      nextLineIndex: 6
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "Yeah, I\u2019ve read through the previous reports here and there,
        though not this version yet. Why bring it up?"
      nextLineIndex: 12
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: Oh? They still make those things?
      nextLineIndex: 16
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I guess I never really pried into it, but, if you don\u2019t mind my asking,
      why do you hate the place so much?"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: I hated the pollution, and I hated the people there more.
      nextLineIndex: 7
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: The cities were too crowded. Noisy too. Felt like my ears were
        constantly bleeding. Compare that to here? The difference between heaven
        and hell.
      nextLineIndex: 8
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "I don\u2019t want to talk about it."
      nextLineIndex: 11
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Some people can be\u2026 troublesome. The best kind of people are the
      ones who comply with the rules and regulations."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 20
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: albert_unep_report
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "That I agree with. No crowds\u2026 no noise\u2026 It\u2019s hard to miss
      what isn\u2019t here on the SUNSET16."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 9
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Besides, jobs in space\u2014and especially jobs under the DOLOS Corporation\u2014are
      few and far between."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 10
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Strict rules and regulations need to be followed. But you and I are both
      good at that.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 20
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: albert_unep_report
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "We all have our demons. You can keep your secrets\u2026"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 20
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: albert_unep_report
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: I figured it would have been useful information to know.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: The only information I need to keep myself updated on is regarding
        the SUNSET16 and/or important updates within the DOLOS Corporation and Erebus
        Holdings.
      nextLineIndex: 13
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "Can\u2019t fault you there. If you have a copy, send it my way."
      nextLineIndex: 15
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "That\u2019s a good response. I like that. Everything you and I need to
      know is on this ship."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 14
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Though it\u2019s nice to gossip about international events here and there,
      after all, the DOLOS corporation has a dominant worldwide reach."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 20
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: albert_unep_report
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Sure, just give me one moment\u2026"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 20
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: albert_unep_report
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Surprisingly so. According to recent DOLOS intel, the environmental reports
      are influenced by companies like Terra Consulting, allowing them to continue
      their\u2026 environmental ventures without intervention."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Doesn\u2019t sound like much of a secret if the DOLOS higher-ups
        know about it."
      nextLineIndex: 17
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: Maybe I should brush up on those files and give them a read.
      nextLineIndex: 19
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "You\u2019d be right about that. Between you, me, and other DOLOS employees,
      our Life-Sciences Division\u2014which you can thank for the AEGIS-1 Collar\u2014will
      be planning something with that group in the future."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "And that would be\u2026?"
      nextLineIndex: 18
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Classified. At least for now.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 20
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: albert_unep_report
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I\u2019ll send you the file in a moment."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 20
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: albert_unep_report
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Anyways, gotta get some rest. DOLOS has already queued tomorrow\u2019s
      schedule. Night, Andy."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Goodnight, Al.
      nextLineIndex: 21
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: 
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: -1
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
